data.title: Shanghai Dragons Gamsu And CoMa Go Hiking: Access Granted
data.description: Matt “Mr. X” Morello picks up Gamsu And CoMa from the Shanghai Dragons to go on a hike in the Hollywood Hills. Find out what it’s like adjusting to life in Los Angeles while playing in the Overwatch League and meet Gamsu’s puppy Uni. This is Access Granted presented by Toyota.

data.title: Chillin’ with Geguri and Danny Lim
data.description: Lover of ice cream, Twitter, frogs, and dogs, there are many unique qualities to Kim “Geguri” Se-Yeon. Danny Lim gets the scoop on what’s next for the Shanghai Dragons tank player.

data.title: The Battle of LA
data.description: Shields Up or Wings Out? The Los Angeles Gladiators and the Los Angeles Valiant have historically duked it out at the Blizzard Arena to see who owns the City of Angels. Who will win this time around?

data.title: Vancouver Titans – Bad Boys of The Overwatch League
data.description: If winning begets confidence, the flawless Vancouver Titans are swimming in swag. Danny Lim talks to Bumper, Haksal, Seominsoo, and Slime about the team’s tenacity, the turbulent Stage 1 finals, and their attitudes moving forward.

data.title: Chendu Hunters Cooking Challenge: Jinmu vs Ameng
data.description: Who knew Jinmu and Ameng of the Chengdu Hunters could serve up authentic Chinese cooking as well as they pop off on the Overwatch League stage? Who will win the battle of the Chengdu Kitchen?

data.title: Inside The Comms | Stage 1 Finals
data.description: With so much on the line for both teams in the Stage 1 Finals, we wanted to hear how crazy it was being part of the fight between the Vancouver Titans and the San Francisco Shock. Listen first hand as confidence falls to cowardice and how the humble become heroes.

data.title: Goodbye, Dafran
data.description: Atlanta Reign announced that Daniel “dafran” Francesca would no longer continue in the Overwatch League. We wanted to highlight some of the best moments with a nice “Goodbye, dude.”
